<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٨٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4206">‌ابْنُ مُعَاذٍ، </a>ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6217">‌أَبِي </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةَ </a>بِهَذَا الْحَدِيثِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ فِيهِ:</span> <span class="c2">«وَلَا يَؤُمُّ الرَّجُلُ الرَّجُلَ فِي سُلْطَانِهِ»</span>. قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2577">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٢٨⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَكَذَا قَالَ يَحْيَى الْقَطَّانُ عَنْ شُعْبَةَ:</span> أَقْدَمُهُمْ قِرَاءَةً.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>